{"tid":539594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實南亞人邊忽得罪你班連登仔？","createTime":"2018-01-24T16:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T17:00:29.000Z","uid":12521,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"91e05a622a5f8b1fc53cf9c45f097ff2ac751c33","tid":539594,"uid":12521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"南亞人都有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我朋友都係南亞人<br />\n佢依家入埋UST 好努力咁融入呢個社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解個個都要用有色眼鏡去睇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nदक्षिण एशियाई अच्छे लोग हैं<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nमेरे दोस्त सभी दक्षिण एशियाई हैं<br />\nघर के अनुसार ड्रेनेज दबाने के लिए यूटीई के अच्छे प्रयासों a एक समुदाय में हे <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nपॉइंट समाधान को व्यक्ति को देखने के लिए रंगीन चश्मे का उपयोग करना चाहिए <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434542daf0920a448ccce454142b39a37f7932c6","tid":539594,"uid":32973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"姦淫虜掠樣樣齊"},{"pid":"7e9b4f69287bf7a7128eacc6343dea6097f96578","tid":539594,"uid":12521,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"हांगकांग के मेरे दक्षिण एशियाई डिपार्टमेंट के अच्छे भोजन से ईर्ष्या रहती है?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9c590646708dc8d23acdc4f774191322d43617","tid":539594,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73a3c87264d584b5a891c7ab5b047f9e9fbf4a64","tid":539594,"ui